
This is the CHANGES file of the PAHFIT distribution

Version 1.2
===========

 - More sane report output format, including reduced Chi-Sq.
 - Add PAHFIT_MAIN_FEATURE_POWER, for computing blended feature
   powers.
 - Update documentation headers.

Version 1.1
===========

 - Input wavelength for PAHFIT is in the *observed frame*, with the
   REDSHIFT used to correct it.  All fits are still performed in the
   rest frame.
 - Refined central position and widths for several dust features.
 - Added "19um" dust feature centered at 18.92um.

Version 1.0
===========

 - Minor modifications to the dust feature set.

Version 0.9
===========

 - First release